":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前係睇到？定一影完已經灰色？</blockquote><br />\n冇留意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前試過，係一開始已經load唔到張相，相信係影果刻根本影唔到。<br />\n除咗咁，camera roll時不時會無哂d相，然後再reload.....無限loop<br />\n最後要剷機先可以再影相"},{"pid":"b25293a91d3f3be4078a89ee2fbfbbd7d8a92ca5","tid":284723,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:46:11.000Z","msg":"個電話ram定唔知咩storage 野唔夠位，用得耐係會咁生滿垃圾爆晒<br />\n相呢就唔好諗了，2000%變唔番出黎，因為根本save唔成功<br />\n<br />\n番到香港full backup (幾十GB) 部iPhone落電腦, 然後reset as new iPhone 再入番backup落去續命啦<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係呢個情況會繼續經常發生，所有有database既都會hang, 如相、歌、Whatsapp<br />\n<br />\n利申：又係旅行個時GG過"},{"pid":"794f369cdac7c83f954e8631941dc5c67b41dde9","tid":284723,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:21:52.000Z","msg":"灰灰的天　空空的街　千串細雨點<br />\n用斜紋交織出一張冷冷面"},{"pid":"05d0eeffee9d35372264e2f266e414e8300a8bf4","tid":284723,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:25:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2455241080fd321de0d287f0e04c6a3320f76ccf","tid":284723,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:53:44.000Z","msg":"iphone悲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1fbd4cb2dfb5ebe3733b6e7e0dd0ad4c1112e0","tid":284723,"uid":12585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:01:07.000Z","msg":"我試過<br />\n係del啲apps去突啲位出嚟，然後部機冇咁lag，正常翻"},{"pid":"9458a56f8086c1c32c9a01a06e6f11b77a6a985e","tid":284723,"uid":12804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"樓主係秦國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd86d7656c2d5a27dd5955d8c72dacb16a337c0","tid":284723,"uid":3727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:10:37.000Z","msg":"認真試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"